java.io.Serializable, java.security.spec.AlgorithmParameterSpec
public class ECF2mKoblitz
extends ECF2mGroupParams

Koblitz curve is an extended elliptic curve. In addition to the regular curve, Koblitz curve also contains the order of the subgroup and cofactor.

Author:
Cryptography and Computer Security Research Group Department of Computer Science Bar-Ilan University (Moriya Farbstein)
